snippet.title: The Door That Insults You When You Pull Instead of Push
snippet.description:
The pinnacle of engineering has arrived. This needed to be done.

Doors have been able to be pushed, pulled, rotated and spread. But now, there is a robot that will revolutionize how embarrassing it is to perform the incorrect action to open the door. I'm sorry.
tags: when you only know 1 line of code
when you only know 1 line of code but you gotta make google
